<h2>Why we created Ratafire?</h2>

	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">We help artists and researchers afford the time for creative freedom.</p>

	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Let us break it down:</p>

		<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><i>Help artists and researchers</i>: we serve artists and researchers and their fans.</p>

		<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><i>Afford the time</i>: many art creation processes and researches can now be conducted on computers instead of on capital centric studios and labs, therefore, we want to make it easy for artists and researchers to have time to work on these artists creations and researches.</p>

		<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><i>Creative freedom</i>: we enable funding for the creative process instead of the outcome, which enhances creative freedom.</p>

